# Snowflake & Power BI: Data-Driven Analytics Design

## Overview
This project examines how Snowflake integrates with Microsoft Power BI to
support scalable analytics and real-time decision-making workflows.

## Problem
Retail and enterprise organizations require a BI architecture that handles
large datasets with performance and flexibility.

## Approach
- Snowflake database and schema design
- Dimensional modeling with star schema
- SQL-based aggregation in place of data cubes
- Power BI for visualization and analysis

## Skills Demonstrated
- Snowflake architecture and SQL
- Power BI integration
- Data warehousing and OLAP strategy

